  # [Podman kube rootless quadlet with user mapping](https://serverfault.com/questions/1166050/podman-kube-rootless-quadlet-with-user-mapping)
  
  [Ask Question](https://serverfault.com/questions/ask)
  
  Asked1 year, 7 months ago
  
  Modified [1 year, 7 months ago](https://serverfault.com/questions/1166050/podman-kube-rootless-quadlet-with-user-mapping?lastactivity "2024-10-17 19:47:19Z")
  
